data.description: WOW! Updated 5-bedroom home that offers 2,945 sq.ft of living space. All bedrooms are very spacious. Home is at the beginning of the cul-de-sac and a greenbelt back yard. From entering the home, you are greeted with a welcoming foyer. Open concept living room, kitchen and formal dining. Enjoy the huge kitchen island that can sit 5! Modern white and gray kitchen cabinets with new backsplash. Refrigerator and dishwasher are less than a year old. Home offers 3.5 baths that have new wood tile flooring. Washer and Dryer will convey. HOA covers all ground maintenance that includes front and backyard landscaping, mulch, trash pickup, community center with gym and pool. Come see this amazing friendly neighborhood that is very peaceful with walking trails that go behind the townhomes. Zoned to York County Schools. Near Newtown, Williamsburg outlets, William and Mary University and other shopping centers.
